 cable TV.</p><p>A fridge and coffee maker are provided in every light-colored room at The Pickwick Hotel San Francisco. The spacious rooms offer a bathrobe and hairdryer for guest convenience. Video games are also available.</p><p>Serving Italian and Mediterranean cuisine, guests of The Pickwick can dine at SOMA Restaurant and Bar.</p><p>Fitness and business facilities are located at Hotel Pickwick. A tour desk and concierge services are also available. If guests wish to pay via third party payment, please contact the hotel five days in advance in order to receive a credit card authorization form.</p><p>This hotel is 0.5 miles from the Museum of Modern Art, and 2.5 miles from Alcatraz Cruises. Fisherman’s Wharf is just 10 minutes'' drive away.</p><p>Union Square is a great choice for travellers interested in shopping, city trips and restaurants.</p>', null, null, 'ChIJRWYNhYaAhYARGVkqbV53to8', 'Stay in the heart of San Francisco', '["http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61894981.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61894922.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896358.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61895152.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61895137.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/918/9187234.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/540/54090032.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896757.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896924.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896600.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/540/54090021.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61895174.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61897133.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896572.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/326/32604089.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/618/61896610.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/imag