anicured gardens, the hotel offers a 24 hour reception.Other amenities include various guest lounge areas, a ticket service and a tour desk. The property offers free parking</p><p>Each room includes a flat-screen TV, ironing facilities, a mini bar, an in-room safe, a dining area and tea/coffee making facilities. Some rooms have a Nespresso coffee machine. All rooms offer a private bathroom with a shower, hairdryer and bathrobes</p>', null, null, 'ChIJh3bewyLcG24RQO-5CRuvJdU', null, '["http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34008079.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34007985.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34011232.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010676.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010659.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413620.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413622.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413623.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413624.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34008002.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010620.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010671.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413625.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413628.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413631.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/334/33413633.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010773.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010798.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010805.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010897.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010851.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34010944.jpg","http://r-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/840x460/340/34011013.jpg","http://q-ec.bstatic.com/images/hotel/8