d a fully equipped kitchen. Meals can be enjoyed indoors or outdoors by the pool. Fitted with a bath or shower, the private bathrooms also includes a hairdryer and free toiletries.</p><p>At Tropicana Pool Villa Jomtien, guests can relax at the terrace and on the sun loungers by the pool while enjoying views of the garden. Other services such as bicycle and car rental arrangements and airport pick-up services are both available for an extra charge. Guests can also make use of the free barbecue facilities and table tennis.</p><p>The villa is a short drive from the beachfront restaurants and bars. It is 3.9 miles away from Underwater World Pattaya while Walking Street Pattaya is 7.2 miles away.</p><p>For additional convenience, guests can sample delectable Asian meals prepared by the in-house chef.</p>', null, null, 'ChIJTY6xGYaWAjERlkw5WleP4O8', null, '[]', '2016-11-23 17:38:59', '2016-11-23 17:38:59', 12.896157399153665, 100.88015288114548, 'Tropicana Pool Villa', null, '+66 99 112 9244', 4.00, null, '692522fd-9937-45e1-87a8-fcebf2762913', 'http://www.tropicanapoolvilla.com/', null, false, null, null, null);
